{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"placement would be laid out vertically.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"symbolKind":"case"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","abstract":[{"text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"placement would be laid out vertically.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}]}}}